<document name="PostRegistrationLetterWithPaymentInstructions">
<xmlData>
<paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Dear </font><font><field name="Registration:FirstName"/></font><font> and Parents of </font><font><field name="Registration:FirstName"/></font><font>,</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>You have successfully registered for this season's Dirt Bowl.  </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Don't forget to send in your signed Medical Waiver. No player can practice or play </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>until their Medical Waiver has been received. </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>If you haven't already paid online, please send a check for $</font><font><field name="SignupFeeForIndividual"/></font><font> payable to "Dirt Bowl".</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Both the payment and the waiver can be mailed to the following address:</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="720" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Dirt Bowl</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="720" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><field name="AdminAdrss"/></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="720" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><field name="AdminsCity"/></font><sp/><font><field name="AdminState"/></font><font>, </font><font><field name="AdminsZIP"/></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="720" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>If you need any information about the season, you can always look at our Web site </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>at http://www.dirtbowl.com.  For dealing with personal information like reviewing or </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>changing your registration info, checking your team roster or schedule and the like, </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>use the link below.  This is your personal link.  Do not share it with others.</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Here it is:  </font><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="PlayerDash" project="" private="true"><authenticationTokenValue><string field="Registration:RegID"/>
</authenticationTokenValue>Player's Dashboard</invitation></u></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>To save this link, click on it.  A Dirt Bowl Web page will come up, your personal page. </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Saving this link depends upon which browser you use:</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="720" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>If you use Internet Explorer, click on "Favorites" in the Menu Bar at top and </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="720" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>then "Add to Favorites."</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="720" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>If you use Firefox, click on "Bookmarks" in the Menu Bar at top and then </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="720" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>"Bookmark this Page."</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="720" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>If you use Safari, click on "Bookmarks" and then "Add Bookmarks."</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>You'll get your team roster and schedule by email once they've been completed, but </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>they will also always be available to you on your Dashboard.</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>I'm looking forward to seeing you at the Dirt Bowl games this season!</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Yours,</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><field name="AdminName"/></font></paragraph>
</xmlData>
</document>
<document name="AdminRegNotification">
<xmlData>
<paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>A registration form has been received for </font><font><field name="Registration:FirstName"/></font><sp/><font><field name="Registration:LastName"/></font><font>. Here is the registration info:</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><table indent="735"><row><cell width="2205"><division indent="0" align="right"><font><b>Player's Name:</b></font></division></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="Registration:FirstName"/></font><sp/><font><field name="Registration:LastName"/></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"><division indent="0" align="right"><font><b>Date of Birth:</b></font></division></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="Registration:RegAgeMo"/></font><font>/</font><font><field name="Registration:RegAgeDay"/></font><font>/</font><font><field name="Registration:RegAgeYr"/></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"><division indent="0" align="right"><font><b>Sex:</b></font></division></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="Registration:Sex"/></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"><division indent="0" align="right"><font><b>Parent's Name:</b></font></division></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="Registration:ParentFirstName"/></font><sp/><font><field name="Registration:ParentLastName"/></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"><division indent="0" align="right"><font><b>Address:</b></font></division></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="Registration:Address"/></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="Registration:City"/></font><font>, CA </font><font><field name="Registration:Zip"/></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"><division indent="0" align="right"><font><b>Email:</b></font></division></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="Registration:ParentEmail"/></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"><division indent="0" align="right"><font><b>Additional Email:</b></font></division></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="Registration:ParentEmail2"/></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"><division indent="0" align="right"><font><b>Phone 1:</b></font></division></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="Registration:Phone1"/></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"><division indent="0" align="right"><font><b>Phone 2:</b></font></division></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="Registration:Phone2"/></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"><division indent="0" align="right"><font><b>Phone 3:</b></font></division></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="Registration:Phone3"/></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"><division indent="0" align="right"><font><b>Friends Requested:</b></font></division></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="Registration:Friend:a"/></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><font><field name="Registration:Friend:b"/></font><sp/><sp/><font><field name="Registration:Friend:c"/></font><sp/></division></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"><division indent="0" align="right"><font><b>Shirt Size:</b></font></division></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="Registration:UniformSize"/></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"><division indent="0" align="right"><font><b>Medical Plan Name:</b></font></division></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="Registration:MedPlanName"/></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="2205"><division indent="0" align="right"><font><b>Plan Number:</b></font></division></cell><cell width="330"></cell><cell width="7530"><division indent="0" align="left"><font><field name="Registration:MedPlanNumber"/></font></division></cell></row></table><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000000">In case of loss, here is the link to </font><font color="000000"><field name="Registration:FirstName"/></font><font color="000000">'s private </font><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="PlayerDash" project="" private="true"><authenticationTokenValue><string field="Registration:RegID"/>
</authenticationTokenValue>Player Dashboard</invitation></u></font><font color="000000">.</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph>
</xmlData>
</document>
<document name="PlayerDashboardReminder">
<xmlData>
<paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Dear </font><font><field name="PlayerFirst"/></font><font> and Parents of </font><font><field name="PlayerFirst"/></font><font>,</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Your personal Dirt Bowl link is </font><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="PlayerDash" project="" private="true"><authenticationTokenValue><string field="PlayerID"/>
</authenticationTokenValue>here</invitation></u></font><font>.  Clicking on this link will take you to </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>your private Dirt Bowl Player Dashboard.</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000000">To save this link, click on it.  A Dirt Bowl Web page will come up, your personal page. </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000000">Saving this link depends upon which brower you use:</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="720" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000000">If you use Internet Explorer, click on "Favorites" in the Menu Bar at top and </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="720" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000000">then "Add to Favorites."</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="720" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000000">If you use Firefox, click on "Bookmarks" in the Menu Bar at top and then </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="720" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000000">"Bookmark this Page."</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="720" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000000">If you use Safari, click on "Bookmarks" and then "Add Bookmarks."</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Be sure to save this link in a safe place.  You can use it to review or </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>change your registration and to see personal information, such as your </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>team assignment and team roster, season schedule and the like.</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>For general information about Dirt Bowl, you can always go to: </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000080"><u><link>
<description>
<string value="http://www.dirtbowl.com"/>
</description>
<url>
<string value="http://www.dirtbowl.com"/>
</url>
</link>
</u></font><font>.</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Yours,</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><field name="AdminName"/></font></paragraph>
</xmlData>
</document>
<document name="Message">
<xmlData>
<paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font size="280" color="AE0000"><b><i><field name="Message"/></i></b></font></paragraph>
</xmlData>
</document>
<document name="Roster Selection Criteria">
<xmlData>
<paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font size="240"><b>Registration Records - Team Rosters</b></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="RegFormManagement" project="">Back to Registration Management</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="AdminDash" project="">Back to Administrator Dashboard</invitation></u></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowWaiverPaymentFields" project="">Waivers &amp; Payments</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowRosterCriteria" project="">Team Rosters</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowContactFields" project="">Contact Info</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowMedicalFields" project="">Medical Info</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowAllFields" project="">All Fields</invitation></u></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><itemization-table version="1"><number-of-columns>7</number-of-columns><column><header>Team</header><contents><field name="Record:Team:TeamId" /></contents></column><column><header>First</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:FirstName" /></contents></column><column><header>Last</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:LastName" /></contents></column><column><header>Age</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:PlayerAge" /></contents></column><column><header>Jersey</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:UniformSize" /></contents></column><column><header>Waiver</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:WaiverReceived" /></contents></column><column><header>Paid</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:PaymentReceived" /></contents></column><conditions><form name="Team" /><form name="Registration" /><conditions>
<equals field="Record:Registration:TeamId">
<string field="Record:Team:TeamId"/>
</equals>
</conditions></conditions></itemization-table></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="RegFormManagement" project="">Back to Registration Management</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="AdminDash" project="">Back to Administrator Dashboard</invitation></u></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowWaiverPaymentFields" project="">Waivers &amp; Payments</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowRosterCriteria" project="">Team Rosters</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowContactFields" project="">Contact Info</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowMedicalFields" project="">Medical Info</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowAllFields" project="">All Fields</invitation></u></font></paragraph>
</xmlData>
</document>
<document name="Contact Fields">
<xmlData>
<paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font size="240"><b>Registration Records - Contact Info</b></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="RegFormManagement" project="">Back to Registration Management</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="AdminDash" project="">Back to Administrator Dashboard</invitation></u></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowWaiverPaymentFields" project="">Waivers &amp; Payments</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowRosterCriteria" project="">Team Rosters</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowContactFields" project="">Contact Info</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowMedicalFields" project="">Medical Info</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowAllFields" project="">All Fields</invitation></u></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><itemization-table version="1"><number-of-columns>11</number-of-columns><column><header>First</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:FirstName" /></contents></column><column><header>Last</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:LastName" /></contents></column><column><header>Parent</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:ParentFirstName" /></contents></column><column><header>Phone 1</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:Phone1" /></contents></column><column><header>Phone 2</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:Phone2" /></contents></column><column><header>Phone 3</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:Phone3" /></contents></column><column><header>Address</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:Address" /></contents></column><column><header>City</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:City" /></contents></column><column><header>Zip</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:Zip" /></contents></column><column><header>Email</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:ParentEmail" /></contents></column><column><header>Email 2</header><contents><field name="Record:Registration:ParentEmail2" /></contents></column><conditions><form name="Registration" /></conditions></itemization-table></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="RegFormManagement" project="">Back to Registration Management</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="AdminDash" project="">Back to Administrator Dashboard</invitation></u></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowWaiverPaymentFields" project="">Waivers &amp; Payments</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowRosterCriteria" project="">Team Rosters</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowContactFields" project="">Contact Info</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowMedicalFields" project="">Medical Info</invitation></u></font><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowAllFields" project="">All Fields</invitation></u></font></paragraph>
</xmlData>
</document>
<document name="Medical Info">
